data.description: Ready to add another house to your portfolio? Investors and Homeowners alike, take a look! This one owner property offers an inviting location nestled in a great neighborhood. The house itself is built on a solid foundation, ensuring durability, and awaits your personal touch with some minor updating/repairs and new carpeting of your choice. It's a worthwhile project for those looking to modernize or simply add a little tender loving care. While this home needs all new carpeting prior to your move in date, it's structure appears sound and sturdy and the home appears to be in overall good condition with just a few minor repairs needed. It's a great as-is investment.
